Date: Mon, 20 Apr 2026 18:34:23 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 7/8] animate hero callouts on page load
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Stagger the hero margin notes in from the sides as the page mounts —
each slides in from its resting direction with its own delay:
- HEADLINES & BUTTONS slides in from the left at 0.35s
- PRICE & OFFERS slides in from the right at 0.65s
- CHECKOUT EXPERIENCE slides in from below at 0.95s
- ANALYSIS_LIVE readout fades+scales in at 1.25s

Cubic-bezier easing (0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) for natural deceleration. On
mobile the stacked callouts below the hero also stagger in at 0.35/
0.55/0.75s so the effect carries across form factors.

prefers-reduced-motion: animation is disabled entirely, callouts land
at their final state so users who've opted out of motion still see the
page correctly.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
